 keep adding to the mortality rates.
 However, the analysis shows that the impact is not sustained in the long
 run.
 The victims that were impacted are only the first wave of victims, and
 the mechanism took place in a few years.
 This suggests that the unintended consequences estimated by the current
 paper and 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
